3663 - Radio and Television Broadcasting and Communications Equipment Summary > KONGSBERG MARITIME PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover radio and television broadcasting and communications equipment. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. KONGSBERG MARITIME PTY LTD is headquartered in Fremantle, Western Australia. It is headed by general manager & managing director Jamie Robert Kilsby. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $32.76 million. Its net profit totalled $1.72 million. KONGSBERG MARITIME PTY LTD forms part of the manufacturing industry sector.
